  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MERIDIAN - Fitness VR Experience. Warm-up routine targeting fascia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s simple: follow and focus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run with OpenXR</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SFX IS CURRENTLY MISSING, ENJOY YOUR OWN MUSIC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your body is connected by fascia, also known as connective tissue or muscle chains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn the way your fascia is used in simple movements, it can make your life much more fluid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can fly around and choose any angle, choose your preferred speed. I also suggest you use small dumbbells at some point. Just focus on the flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SET 1 is accessible for all</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I want everyone to engage! Moves are safe and suit all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hope you give it a try and enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created by Alexander Kosenko.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MERIDIAN.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sources:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jordan Terry \"Adaptable Polarity\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thomas Myers \"Anatomy Trains\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072410/extras/5482dd613c9ff658983f3696a5f88cd1.avif?t=1747053845\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072410/extras_big/5482dd613c9ff658983f3696a5f88cd1.avif?t=1747053845 width=800 height=400 /></span>                                                                        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MERIDIAN - Fitness VR Experience. Warm-up routine targeting fascia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s simple: follow and focus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run with OpenXR</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SFX IS CURRENTLY MISSING, ENJOY YOUR OWN MUSIC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your body is connected by fascia, also known as connective tissue or muscle chains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn the way your fascia is used in simple movements, it can make your life much more fluid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can fly around and choose any angle, choose your preferred speed. I also suggest you use small dumbbells at some point. Just focus on the flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SET 1 is accessible for all</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I want everyone to engage! Moves are safe and suit all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hope you give it a try and enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created by Alexander Kosenko.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MERIDIAN.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sources:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jordan Terry \"Adaptable Polarity\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thomas Myers \"Anatomy Trains\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072410/extras/5482dd613c9ff658983f3696a5f88cd1.avif?t=1747053845\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072410/extras_big/5482dd613c9ff658983f3696a5f88cd1.avif?t=1747053845 width=800 height=400 /></span>                                                                        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
